comments: Connaughton (MIL) makes hand-on-ball contact to dislodge the ball from Anderson (MEM).
Morant (MEM) makes knee-to-knee contact with DiVincenzo (MIL) at the end of the drive, which affects his SQBR.
Valanciunas (MEM) could be deemed to be imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Connaughton (MIL) rests his forearm on Valanciunas' (MEM) body during the layup attempt, and the contact is marginal.
Winslow (MEM) makes marginal contact with Middleton's (MIL) arm after the release that does not affect his driving shot attempt.

Replay review of the foul called on Antetokounmpo (MIL) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Antetokounmpo (MIL) moves laterally and delivers contact with his forearm into Morant's (MEM) body during his driving shot attempt.

Holiday (MIL) maintains a legal defensive position in front of Morant (MEM) as he dribbles and lowers his shoulder into Holiday's front. As Holiday absorbs the marginal contact initiated by Morant, Holiday makes clean contact with the ball and deflects the ball away from Morant.
Winslow (MEM) legally contests Connaughton's (MIL) jump shot attempt.
Holiday (MIL) is established in Brooks' (MEM) path and absorbs the body contact during the driving shot attempt.
Replay review of the play confirmed the on-court ruling of goaltending. Antetokounmpo (MIL) makes contact with the ball after it has reached its apex and is on its downward flight.
DiVincenzo (MIL) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Brooks' (MEM) path and does not deliver any contact.
Middleton (MIL) makes marginal contact with Winslow (MEM) as he releases from Winslow at the end of the drive.
Middleton (MIL) draws Winslow (MEM) into the air and Winslow makes contact with Middleton during his jump shot attempt.

After the release on his driving shot attempt, Morant's (MEM) momentum carries him towards Antetokounmpo (MIL), causing incidental body contact to occur as Antetokounmpo jumps vertically and absorbs it.
DiVincenzo (MIL) makes marginal contact with Morant's (MEM) lower body during his driving shot attempt.
Holiday's (MIL) off-arm extends slightly as he releases away from the contact with Brooks (MEM) at the end of his drive, and the contact is marginal.
Brooks (MEM) legally contests Holiday's (MIL) jump shot attempt.
Connaughton (MIL) legally contests Bane's (MEM) jump shot attempt.
